        <abstract> 
<p>Cites article by David Forbes dealing with the geology of the S. American Cordillera ["Geology of Bolivia and South Peru", <hi rend="italic">Q. J. Geol. Soc. Lond.</hi> 17 (1861): 7–62].</p> 
            <p>Discusses the flexures of the Cordillera, the age of the mountains, and basaltic dikes in granite areas.</p>
